lon Tower]], [[Niagara Falls, Ontario]], Canada}}\n|align=left|\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|17\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} Matthew Green\n|KO\n|2 {{small|(6)}}\n|{{small|23/06/2000}}\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Grand Casino Biloxi|Grand Casino]], [[Biloxi, Mississippi]]}}\n|align=left|\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|16\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} John Rainwater\n|TKO\n|3 {{small|(?)}}\n|{{small|25/02/2000}}\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Rhodes-on-the Pawtuxet]], [[Cranston, Rhode Island]]}}\n|align=left|\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|15\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} Gary Winmon\n|TKO\n|1 {{small|(10)}}\n|{{small|17/12/1999}}\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[David L. Lawrence Convention Center|Lawrence Convention Center]], [[Pittsburgh]]}}\n|align=left|\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|14\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} Anthony Green\n|TKO\n|8 {{small|(10)}}\n|{{small|17/09/1999}}\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Flickenger Athletic Center, [[Buffalo, New York]]}}\n|align=left|{{small|Won USA New York State Heavyweight title.}}\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|13\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|Jamaica}} Rowyan Wallace\n|KO\n|2 {{small|(6)}}\n|{{small|04/06/1999}}\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[The Blue Horizon|Blue Horizon]], [[Philadelphia]]}}\n|align=left|\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|12\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} Brian Sargent\n|KO\n|1 {{small|(6)}}\n|{{small|24/04/1999}}\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Portland Art Museum|Arts Museum]], [[Portland, Oregon]]}}\n|align=left|\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|11\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} Dwayne Hall\n|TKO\n|1 {{small|(4)}}\n|{{small|19/02/1999}}\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Turning Stone Resort & Casino|Turning Stone Casino]], [[Verona, New York]]}}\n|align=left|\n|- align=center\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|10\u20130\n|align=left|{{flagicon|USA}} Rodney McSwain\n|TKO\n|3 {{small|(6)}}\n|{{small|03/12/199